  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if Itacitinib in combination with corticosteroids is safe and tolerable in
      patients with Grade IIB-IVD acute graft-versus-host disease (GVHD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
